Package org.wmn4j.notation

Interface Durational

All Known Implementing Classes:
Chord, Note, Rest
public sealed interface Durational permits Note, Rest, Chord
Interface for all the notation objects that have a duration. This interface is not intended to be implemented by classes other than the basic notation classes Note, Rest, and Chord.

All implementations of this interface must be thread-safe.
